@template markdown_tips
{
	@metadata
	{
		guid: '6873aa10-81e7-4a1b-a8f4-a505445397f4',
		type: 'component'
	}
	You also can use advanced Markdown formatting:
	- Tables, Codeblocks, Blockquotes, etc.
	- Math formulas, via `$latex$` or `$$latex$$`
	- Images, via `![alt text](url)`
	When you writing markdown code blocks, user is provided with `copy`, `save` and `execute` buttons, meaning you can provide a code for direct execution.
}

